  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Animal Farming &amp; the Jungle: Reporting from Brazil</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">With this project, Sentient Media launches an investigative journalism arm in Brazil, focused on animal agriculture, environmental and climate effects of intensive farming, and welfare and rights of animals. Brazil is both a key player in global livestock production and the main home of the Amazon rainforest. This potential for conflict is exacerbated by the mounting climate crisis and the lack of political will for necessary action. Compelling, high quality reporting is urgently needed.</narrative>
  </description>
